### **Flowbit Management:**

```
Session Tracking:
â”œâ”€â”€ eternalblue.session.active (Set in Phase 1)
â”œâ”€â”€ eternalblue.phase1.detected (Initial exploitation)
â”œâ”€â”€ eternalblue.phase2.overflow.detected (Buffer overflow)
â”œâ”€â”€ eternalblue.phase3.success.detected (Compromise confirmed)
â””â”€â”€ eternalblue.medical.target (Medical device targeted)
```

### **Threshold Configuration:**

| Rule Type | Threshold | Tracking | Duration |
|-----------|-----------|----------|----------|
| Phase 1 | 1 event | by_src | 120 seconds |
| Phase 2 | 1 event | by_src | 120 seconds |
| Phase 3 | 1 event | by_dst | 300 seconds |
| Correlation | 1 event | by_src | 600 seconds |

